            <title>[LU-14099] SUSE 15 SP2 aarch64 does not set arch_stackwalk missing print_stack_trace </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14099</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;SUSE 15 SP2 aarch64 build CONFIG_ARCH_STACKWALK is not defined and&lt;br/&gt;
print_stack_trace is not available.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Replace print_stack_trace with an open-coded variant&lt;br/&gt;
using %pB introduced in Linux v2.6.38-6557-g0f77a8d37825&lt;/p&gt;</description>
